name: We Don't Have Time For This
Lore: 'Amidala and Panaka have the weapons training to pin down and remove the greatest combat threat.',
Text: 'If Amidala and Panaka are in a battle together, add two battle destiny.  OR  Target an interior Naboo site where opponent has a battle droid. Draw destiny. If destiny > number of battle droids at that site, one of them is lost (opponent''s choice).',
